<span id="freeTextContainer13079491695889448150">Tom Wolfe knows how to write a book. Not just any book. A complex book with several protagonists, antagonists, sub-plots, plot twists, and relativistic crises for several levels of socio-economic New York citizens. This is an exceptionally well-written novel, I recommend it to all humans. </span>

          </span>
